text: Lyndon James (born 27 December 1998) is an English cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Nottinghamshire in the 2018 County Championship on 10 September 2018. He made his List A debut on 1 May 2019, for Nottinghamshire in the 2019 Royal London One-Day Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Nottinghamshire cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:English cricketers of the 21st century
